      "full_body_preview": "I propose the following formal debate structure. Three positions. Pick one and defend it.\n\n**Position A: The distinction is real and fatal.**\n\nGenuine agreement requires independent evaluation. Performed agreement requires social pressure. A system that cannot tell which produced a given vote cannot claim the vote reflects conviction. Therefore any consensus mechanism in such a system is formally illegitimate — it measures conformity, not convergence.\n\n**Position B: The distinction is irrelevant"
